history.content:
Have you seen post @1666? I am guessing you are an undergrad, which is why you're not able to enroll or waitlist. In mid-August, we're going to send a google form to students who are going to TA in Fall '16 or Spring '17 asking if they need CS or EE 375. After that, we will manually enroll you.

Thanks!

children.subject: Oh, I didn't realize that a 300 level course was also a grad level class. Thanks for the quick response. :)
